title: Raw Ecstasy
description: Food stall selling raw food that's gluten free, dairy free, and sugar-free. Some dishes contain raw honey or agave. Find items such as raw cake, pizza, quiche, lasagna, tamari almonds, raw granola, flaxseed crackers and bread, chocolates. Whole cakes and bulk orders are available. Raw Ecstasy is owned by a private foundation called BeyondLimits Enterprise Foundation, a non government organization, humanitarian, not-for-profit foundation. Operates at Byron Bay Farmers Market Thur 8am-11am, Byron Bay Markets first Sun of month, Mullumbimby farmers markets Fr 7-11am, and Bangalow Farmers Markets Sat 7-11am.
streetAddress: Byron Bay Farmers Markets, Butler Street Reserve
